    <description>GitHub audit, governance, and inventory for organizations.

gh-audit produces JSON inventory, HTML reports, and Excel workbooks
for GitHub organization auditing, governance, and inventory analysis.

Features:
- Standard and deep scan profiles
- Multi-organization scanning via YAML config
- GitHub App and PAT authentication
- Offline HTML reports with SVG charts
- Excel workbook with 10 analysis sheets
- GitHub Enterprise Server support

A free tool by N8 Group - DevOps Transformation. Executed with Precision.
https://n8-group.com | sales@n8-group.com</description>
    <summary>GitHub audit, governance, and inventory tool by N8 Group</summary>
